Family Tree
Create a Ruby on Rails 3.x application which allows users to manage their family trees. Requirements:

- Domain model:
  - A Person has the following attributes: name, date of birth
  - A Person is associated with other people in their family tree via Relationships

- UI:
  - Create people and store them in a database (of your choice).
  - Establish and persist relationships among people.
  - View a person and traverse their family tree. The UI design is up to you. Show us what you got!

- Tests:
  - All components must be fully tested
